OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers across the region.
OL,7,FShowers may be heavy, possibly with
OL,8,Fhail and thunder, and merge into
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain at times.
OL,10,FPleasant in any sunshine, but
OL,11,Fotherwise feeling rather cool for June.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing this evening
OL,14,Fto leave late sunny spells. Cool to
OL,15,Fbegin the night under clear skies, but
OL,16,Ftemperatures rebounding slightly as
OL,17,Fcloud builds during the early hours of
OL,18,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
