OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA wet and windy day as rain
OL,6,Fspreads across the region, turning
OL,7,Flocally heavy at times. Feeling muggy
OL,8,Funder widespread cloud cover. Drier by
OL,9,Fthe evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FLargely
OL,12,Fcloudy and breezy on Friday with
OL,13,Fpatchy drizzle. Becoming drier and
OL,14,Fwarmer over the weekend as high
OL,15,Fpressure builds, with winds also
OL,16,Feasing and some sunny spells emerging.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
